text:
I have made multiple orders with strawberrynet and they have never got an order incorrect, they are reliable and safe. Products arrive within a few days every time with a high standard of packaging. The website is easy to you as well as checkout. I get a discount on top of already discounted products every time and never have to pay for shipping. My order is always confirmed via email as well as shipping details.
Love It
